This repostiry contains sevaral part of codes utilized in the exome-seq and metabolomics combination analysis of early-onset schizophrenia. Sevearal parts are included:

1. Pipeline to detect variants and CNVs from exome-seq data
2. Piepline to detect DEMs from LC-MS/MS data
3. In-house R scripts to analyze
  (i) the association between gene variants and clinical symptome scores
  (ii) the corerlation betwwen metabolite intensity and clinical symptome scores
  (iii) the association betwwen gene variants and metabolite intensity
  (iv) construction the protein-metabolite network
